</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Weight Gain Plan (25-40 Underweight)</h1>

        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Breakfast</th>
                <th>Lunch</th>
                <th>Snacks</th>
                <th>Dinner</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Scrambled eggs with avocado on whole wheat toast</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken with quinoa and roasted vegetables</td>
                <td>Greek yogurt with honey and mixed nuts</td>
                <td>Baked salmon, mashed sweet potatoes, and green salad</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Oatmeal with almond butter and banana</td>
                <td>Grilled turkey with brown rice and steamed broccoli</td>
                <td>A handful of almonds and a protein shake</td>
                <td>Stir-fried tofu with whole wheat noodles and vegetables</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Whole grain pancakes with peanut butter and honey</td>
                <td>Grilled fish with quinoa and steamed asparagus</td>
                <td>Avocado toast with cottage cheese</td>
                <td>Chicken curry with brown rice and sautéed spinach</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Greek yogurt with granola and mixed berries</td>
                <td>Grilled shrimp with couscous and roasted carrots</td>
                <td>Handful of walnuts and an apple</td>
                <td>Baked tofu with mashed sweet potatoes and sautéed mushrooms</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Egg and cheese sandwich on whole wheat bread</td>
                <td>Grilled salmon with wild rice and steamed peas</td>
                <td>Low-fat cottage cheese with flaxseeds</td>
                <td>Stir-fried chicken with whole grain pasta and spinach</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Avocado smoothie with protein powder</td>
                <td>Brown rice with grilled chicken and sautéed green beans</td>
                <td>Hummus with whole grain crackers</td>
                <td>Grilled fish with roasted sweet potatoes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Oatmeal with flaxseeds and cinnamon</td>
                <td>Vegetable stir-fry with tofu and quinoa</td>
                <td>Mixed nuts and herbal tea</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken with brown rice and steamed broccoli</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Workout</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Strength training (upper body) + Light cardio (20 min)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Strength training (lower body) + Yoga for flexibility</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Full-body strength training + Core workouts</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Brisk walking (20 min) + Light stretching</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Strength training (upper body) + Cycling (20 min)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Strength training (lower body) + Core workouts</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Rest day or light stretching and meditation</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
